response.original_title: 理芽 2nd ONE-MAN LIVE 「ニューロマンスII」
response.overview: SINKA LIVE SERIES EP.Ⅳ RIM 2nd ONE-MAN LIVE "NEUROMANCE Ⅱ -  Kamitsubaki City AREA 1- " is confirmed to be held in a virtual live event.  It’s been 2 and a half years since the release of the last album. This event features the latest album "NEW ROMANCER2." and marks the 2nd solo live event.  After her 1st solo live event, RIM, who has since had numerous releases and undergone a language study abroad experience in the United States, invites you to witness this "Neuromance."
